<template>
  <v-app>
    <v-card>
      <form>
        <v-text-field
          v-model="name"
          :counter="10"
          label="Name"
          required
          @input="$v.name.$touch()"
          @blur="$v.name.$touch()"
        ></v-text-field>
        <v-text-field
          v-model="email"
          label="E-mail"
          required
          @input="$v.email.$touch()"
          @blur="$v.email.$touch()"
        ></v-text-field>
        <v-select
          v-model="select"
          :items="items"
          label="Item"
          required
          @change="$v.select.$touch()"
          @blur="$v.select.$touch()"
        ></v-select>
        <v-checkbox
          v-model="checkbox"
          label="Do you agree?"
          required
          @change="$v.checkbox.$touch()"
          @blur="$v.checkbox.$touch()"
        ></v-checkbox>

        <v-btn class="mr-4" @click="submit"> submit </v-btn>
        <v-btn @click="clear"> clear </v-btn>
      </form>
    </v-card>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
export default {};
</script>

<style></style>
